<section class="mission-section text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="lead">Together, we are committed to ending hunger and creating a world where no one goes to bed hungry.</p>
      <p>We believe that everyone deserves access to nutritious food and a chance for a better future.</p>
      <a href="#donate" class="btn btn-lg cta-button">Donate Now</a>
